														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-276490">
									

<p>Thanks. I wrote this one from a different perspective: most SCPs derive horror from how terrible they are, but I focused mainly on trying to make it horrifying mostly by the means necessary to hold it in check. Hope I succeeded: the goal was to create a disquieting feeling in the reader about how far the organization would go.</p>

							</div>

								
					
