														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-441717">
									

<p>"Disquieting" is probably the understatement of the century. I had the fortune of reading the article without knowing anything about this site, and let me tell you, it's quite an experience.</p>
<p>Especially the sudden shift in meaning upon reading the phrase "XK class end-of-the-world scenario", cleverly buried in an addendum.</p>
<p>Well done, sir.</p>
<p>Although I do see room for improvement: "between █ and ██ years of age" narrows it down to around 10. Just say something like "young female of unknown age", and let our imaginations take over from there.</p>

							</div>

								
					
